meta_data.description: answer multiple choice questions about the rules.

questions.question:
Below is a question about the game Wordle. Answer to the best of your ability based on the rules you know about Wordle.
Q: How many letter are in the word you are trying to guess?
A) 4
B) 5
C) 6
D) Any amount
questions.completion: Based on the rules of Wordle, the answer to the question is D) Any amount. The word that the player is trying to guess can be of any length, so there is no specific number of letters.
